  <!-- EN: Adanium -->
  <PM_Adanium.label>精金</PM_Adanium.label>
  <!-- EN: Adanium is a kind of gravitational lattice material derived from Project Purifier. Rather than relying on physical hardness, Adanium encapsulates microscopic singularities to severely curve local spacetime. This "gravity shield" deflects kinetic and beam attacks via lensing effects and shreds targets at the atomic level using immense tidal forces upon contact. Its critical weakness is disintegration weaponry; rupturing the lattice triggers a catastrophic spatial collapse. While retaining a manageable physical mass, the material generates massive spacetime drag, making it impossible for unaugmented humans to wield and restricting its use to heavy machinery and warships. -->
  <PM_Adanium.description>一种源自净化者项目的晶格超材料。精金由人造引力井结构构成，利用重力扭曲攻击，微观结构将逸散的冲击动能与热流引导耗散，从而达到对几乎所有的已知攻击免疫的特性。这种特性使其在常规火力面前坚不可摧，唯一的弱点是破坏结构的解离武器。由于它的引力特性，精金会产生一种时空粘滞感，因此仅被作为重型机械与战舰的主装甲，凡人躯体根本无法承受其带来的物理负荷。</PM_Adanium.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Solarite -->
  <PM_Solarite.label>太阳素</PM_Solarite.label>
  <!-- EN: A hyper-condensed core of fusion energy, harvested directly from an artificial star and stabilized within a crystalline containment unit. Known as Solarite, this substance is the primary power source for advanced Purifier technology. While normally handled by sophisticated converters, the volatile reaction can be crudely initiated by a fission-level event in desperate situations. -->
  <PM_Solarite.description>一种高度浓缩的聚变能量，直接从一颗燃烧的人造恒星中提取，并稳定在一个特制容器内。这种物质被称为太阳素，是大部分净化者机械的能量源。虽然通常由复杂的转换器处理，但在条件不允许的情况下，反应可以由裂变级事件粗略地启动以制造少量的太阳素。</PM_Solarite.description>
  
</LanguageData>